# =====================================================================
# .gitignore para .NET / MAUI / Visual Studio
# Basado en https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore
# =====================================================================

## Carpetas de salida y caches
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/
[Tt]emp/

## Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.userprefs

## Archivos generados por restore / build
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/
*.binlog
.dotnet/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage*/

## ReSharper / dotCover
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user
*.dotCover

## Specific to MAUI / mobile
Resources/Raw/
Resources/Splash/Generated/
*.keystore
*.jks
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
*.cer
*.aab
*.apk
*.ipa
*.appx
*.appxbundle
*.msix
*.msixbundle

## Android
local.properties
*.hprof
.gradle/

## Windows / publish
publish/
PublishProfiles/

## Sistema operativo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## Logs y diagnostico
*.log
*.tlog
*.lastbuildstate
*.cache

## Otros
*.swp
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
node_modules/

.claude
